                     <interp inst="t17830723-121-person1170" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I live in Hoxton-market, the prisoner lives with me; on the 31st of May, he came home about twelve o'clock as near as I can guess.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17830723-121-person1171">
                  WILLIAM
                   SIMFIELD
               <interp inst="t17830723-121-person1171" type="surname" value="SIMFIELD"></interp>
