                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a sawyer I am a lodger; I always thought him a very honest man.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17830723-121-verdict559" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830723-121-verdict559" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
